[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "エスカ",
		"romanized_name": "Escha",
		"model_path_hash": "4942920317009730088",
		"text": "お待たせしました～。\n今日はリンゴのタルトを焼いてきたんです！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8567200502263774699",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "まあ、いい香りね。書類もちょうど一区切り\nついたところだし、休憩にしましょうか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "クーデリア",
		"romanized_name": "Cuderia ",
		"model_path_hash": "5065022776013089089",
		"text": "あたしも手が止まってたところ。\nエスカ、ありがとう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7389579890239046457",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "エスカ",
		"romanized_name": "Escha",
		"model_path_hash": "4942920317009730088",
		"text": "どうぞ、たくさんありますから\n遠慮なく食べてくださいね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8567200502263774699",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "おや、何やら甘い香りがしますね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "エスカ",
		"romanized_name": "Escha",
		"model_path_hash": "4942920317009730088",
		"text": "プラフタさんもどうぞ！　\nリンゴのタルト、焼きたてですよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8567200502263774699",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "ありがとうございます。いただきます",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "そうだ、プラフタさん。あなた、元の世界では\n相当な錬金術の実力者だって聞いたわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "ちょっと相談があるんだけど、いいかしら",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "もちろんです。なんでしょうか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "みんなの動向を、\nもっと正確に把握できる術がないかと悩んでいて……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "何かいい方法、思いつかないかしら",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "そうですね……個々の人物の位置を特定したり、\n我々の仲間とそれ以外を見分ける方法……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "あらかじめ仲間のみに固有の何かを持たせておき、\nそれを探知することで実現できるかもしれません",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "クーデリア",
		"romanized_name": "Cuderia ",
		"model_path_hash": "5065022776013089089",
		"text": "固有のものなら、あるじゃない。\n「飴」よ。みんな必ず持ってるでしょ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7389579890239046457",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "エスカ",
		"romanized_name": "Escha",
		"model_path_hash": "4942920317009730088",
		"text": "あ、確かに！　\n「飴」なら絶対なくさないですもんね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8567200502263774699",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "なるほど。「飴」の位置を世界規模で検知し、\n地図上に表示する機構……理論上は可能です",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "本当に？　\nそれができれば、今抱えてる悩みが一気に解決するわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クーデリア",
		"romanized_name": "Cuderia ",
		"model_path_hash": "5065022776013089089",
		"text": "でも、かなり大掛かりな仕組みになるんじゃない？　\n素材も技術も必要だし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7389579890239046457",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "皆の知識や技術を持ち寄れば、不可能では\nありません。協力者がいれば、実現性は高まります",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "エスカ",
		"romanized_name": "Escha",
		"model_path_hash": "4942920317009730088",
		"text": "わたしも手伝います！　\nみんなで力を合わせれば、きっとできますよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8567200502263774699",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "ありがとう、エスカちゃん。\nクーデリアちゃん、あなたもお願いね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "クーデリア",
		"romanized_name": "Cuderia ",
		"model_path_hash": "5065022776013089089",
		"text": "もちろんよ。こうして物事が効率化されていくのって\n気持ちいいのよね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7389579890239046457",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "では、早速レシピの検討に移ります。\n必要な資料を集めておいていただけると",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "エスカ",
		"romanized_name": "Escha",
		"model_path_hash": "4942920317009730088",
		"text": "はい！　素材も調達してきますね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8567200502263774699",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]